parameters: Let's go!! Match my timing, Akane!!
00_st_akane02_anger
Akane: Take this...!!
Now's the time!!!
Are you alright, Princess!!
00_st_pri_03
Princess Soara: Ugh... Ah... Reisha...?
Thank goodness! You've regained consciousness!!

Yes, that's right. I am Knight Reisha. I apologize for my
tardiness, but I have returned to your side!
00_st_pri_03
Princess Soara: Ugh... grr... the chancellor...

Princess Soara: Stop him... we cannot let things continue
like this... ugh... ahh...!!

Please don't overexert yourself, rest your body for now. I
will take care of everything!
Come on, give up. There's no way out for you now.

Chancellor: No way out, you say? Don't make me laugh. It
seems you're the ones who fail to understand the situation.
00_st_akane02_serious

Akane: Hey hey, still putting on a brave face? What can you
possibly do all by yourself now that you've lost your
precious princess?
Chancellor: I've said it from the beginning.

Chancellor: What I desired was not that 'little girl' over
there, but rather the 'royal blood' itself.
What do you mean by that...?

Chancellor: Think about how much blood has been spilled in
this place every time you cut down those tentacles that were
sucking magic from her.
What are you trying to say with that!!
Chancellor: Kukuku...!!!

Chancellor: A scheme should always be layered two or three
times deep.

Chancellor: The essence of royal bloodline magic lies in the
materialization of immense magical power...!!!

Chancellor: Now, oh tainted blood of the king, gather once
more to this sword!! Here, my knowledge and the royal
bloodline will converge, marking the first step towards
domination!!
Chancellor: Behold with your own eyes!!

Chancellor: Witness the birth of the "Sword of Dawn,"
drenched in blood and hailed as the royal family's greatest
treasure...!!!
